<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>All ZF components should be loosely coupled and be able to be used alone without other components if possible.</p>

<p>Zend_Feed_Builder_Header  for example:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
Zend_Loader::loadClass('Zend_Validate_EmailAddress');
</code></pre>

<p>A simple require_once would be faster and would decouple it from Zend_Loader.</p>

<p>There are a few other places in Zend_Feed where this should also be decoupled.</p>

<p>Zend_Feed (line 380)
Zend_Feed_Builder_Header_Itunes (line 115)
Zend_Feed_Builder_Header (lines 178, 249, 272)</p>

